{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[Dm] Sometimes you're better off [C] dead
There's a [Dm] gun in your hand and it's [C] pointing at your head
You [Dm] think you're mad, too [C] bad
You think you're [Dm] coping, but you're just lined [C] up for the slaughter
[Dm] Collapsing and [C] flowing like water
[Dm] Have you got to it yet? [C] No out of pocket
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_bridge: Pre-Chorus}
