{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[Dm] Too many hands in a [C] crowd
Many [Dm] reasons for any [C] subtext to be loud
[Dm] Inner city [C] pressure
[Dm] Just wait until the [C] morning after
You [Dm] got no future, [C] you got no past
[Dm] Here today, [C] built to last
[Dm] In every city, [C] in every nation
[Dm] From Lake Geneva [C] to the Finland Station
{end_of_verse}

